metadata.name: SWANBOT3000
metadata.description:
the SWANBOT3000, from 2021  - 1 physical print existing. (250g gloss, A1 size, signed and numbered 1/1)  
Exhibited in physical form in the summer of 2021 at ART MONDAY gallery at Vesterbro, Copenhagen. 

The first creation of the portals to the bubbleverse. The first of many to come.
